{"tid":1258321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】陳健波：獨立調查應查示威者資金來源　雨遮下有利器","createTime":"2019-06-26T05:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T06:52:14.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c4168a07793b40b6ba58244ee4159361f9ab0bc4","tid":1258321,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:03:28.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂風波仍未平息。民間提出成立獨立調查委員會調查6.12警方使用過分武力鎮壓事件等多個訴求。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2957781/org/4d9691915345d8cc2da49a1411a2b3b9.jpg/g1uP1_HayABS5HcwPpD0Dz2_bOBH__OtJ-pKgCfqSoA?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2957781%2Forg%2F4d9691915345d8cc2da49a1411a2b3b9.jpg%2Fg1uP1_HayABS5HcwPpD0Dz2_bOBH__OtJ-pKgCfqSoA%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=0212211b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立法會財委會主席陳健波出席港台節目《千禧年代》表示，如獨立調查委員會是公正、合理、廣泛，大家不會反對，「要查吓示威者資金來源」。他指，現時香港面對的最大困難是警隊面對很大壓力，「示威者手上表面上係雨遮，但下面係利器」，警隊怨氣非常重。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，如示威令政府和立法會甚麼都不做，會讓市民受害，「反對派組織咁多示威，一定有政治能量叫停（示威）」；又表示不相信反修例運動沒有大台，「背後一定有人操控」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2957606/org/f5f2ab8cd3297a43a3bc6f216ea10e46.jpg/Gvk2eq4gU_ZGphyCTI_GsQZ4-3X1yvs8myUufrElLn4?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2957606%2Forg%2Ff5f2ab8cd3297a43a3bc6f216ea10e46.jpg%2FGvk2eq4gU_ZGphyCTI_GsQZ4-3X1yvs8myUufrElLn4%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=8418d2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳健波指，現時香港面對的最大困難是警隊面對很大壓力，「示威者手上表面上係雨遮，但下面係利器」，警隊怨氣非常重。（資料圖片/林若勤攝）<br />\n<br />\n陳健波表示，獨立調查委員會如果能用最公平、徹底方式調查，不會有人反對，但他認為，警隊已成為是磨心，怨氣非常重，現時最重要是說服警員，要多做一點事去鼓勵警察。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，大多數警員都希望做「鋤奸、扶正」的工作，而非面對示威；而警員和家人被欺凌，他就形容是喪盡天良，認為如示威者和警方都曾做「過分的事」，就要被調查，並且不應該醜化所有警察，欺凌警員家人。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，如調查對警隊打擊大，只會令香港更不穩，很多無法移民的香港人，都要留在香港受罪。"},{"pid":"7c41722067fb0bffb0d86e49f75d8e1f00cd7258","tid":1258321,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者手上表面上係雨遮，但下面係利器</span><br />\n<br />\n咁撚弱智既野都講得出"},{"pid":"ed9e553e9e57180b70bc71b53358cae89ac1e0ae","tid":1258321,"uid":42364,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96bdRXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96bdRXT.png&h=0b5c6aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n識射死光添呀"},{"pid":"5ee6ce57d383dac30b4f40a7e07cf4086f348738","tid":1258321,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"擺明佢老母個臭閪同佢自己個屎忽卑人插過唔少次啦"},{"pid":"5a1c8c784068f061203a92e16054cf8433304e80","tid":1258321,"uid":54511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:31:11.000Z","msg":"我見呢幾星期 所有高官 答既問題 都極度弱智沒思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實係咪覺得香港人 無腦 先咁答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  下面應該有十大兵器      <br />\n血滴子 摺凳 蕉皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5498e42ae98cfcb84f64683b4936ccd94a9829","tid":1258321,"uid":32502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"d官真係個個離地<br />\n又冇腦<br />\n香港政府真係已經腐敗到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d127f11ea14c0ab0f698e3096a138fdd954e8e9","tid":1258321,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0lFj3yffAQs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0lFj3yffAQs&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=910107c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0lFj3yffAQs</a>"},{"pid":"5757b05870d95d87d1d161a5b95f6eb90edad55d","tid":1258321,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed9e553e9e57180b70bc71b53358cae89ac1e0ae","tid":1258321,"uid":42364,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96bdRXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96bdRXT.png&h=0b5c6aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n識射死光添呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"邊套動漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}